profile: Our family owned business is based out of Kelowna, BC and services the Interior of British Columbia. Okanagan New Age Furnace and Duct Cleaning is a company run with integrity and takes pride in their work. With exceptional customer service and superior cleaning techniques customers will receive an unmatched experience. Our technicians will arrive on site with our portable HYPERVAC. Using suction of 5000 cfm we clean each vent individually. The SCORPION cleaning system uses 165 psi of compressed air blasted through semi-rigid tools to break up dirt, dust and debris in the duct work blowing it all back towards the vacuum. Before and after footage can be shown after the cleaning. Cleaning your ducts and furnace will improve air quality and improve furnace efficiency reducing heating costs.
warranty_terms: We always show the before and after video of the work done
